"children":69},{},[70],{"type":46,"value":71},"I am sick and tried of reading pages and pages of justification on how poor\nNepal is or we are. So helpless and so bound by the situation, we seek HELP.",{"type":17,"tag":18,"props":73,"children":74},{},[75],{"type":46,"value":76},"Let me tell you a real life situation:",{"type":17,"tag":18,"props":78,"children":79},{},[80,82,89],{"type":46,"value":81},"As a child, I have seen beggars begging in the street of ",{"type":17,"tag":22,"props":83,"children":86},{"href":84,"rel":85},"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Road_of_Kathmandu",[26],[87],{"type":46,"value":88},"New\nRoad",{"type":46,"value":90},". Then I use to\nthink, that these beggars will certainly not beg forever. I thought they might\nsome day come out of it when they have enough savings. But I still see the\nsame beggars today, in the same street begging. What a sad story?",{"type":17,"tag":18,"props":92,"children":93},{},[94],{"type":46,"value":95},"Why? And only WHY? Haven't they have had enough of money to be not begging.\nThen I might be criticized that, \"Hey, Deep... They are begging they don't get\nenough so they have to beg again. They don't have saving ACCOUNT. Deep be\nrealistic.\"",{"type":17,"tag":18,"props":97,"children":98},{},[99],{"type":46,"value":100},"EXACTLY. That is my point. Begging doesn't make you rich. It makes you lazy\nand dependable. A parasite. A social parasite. If you need development, you\nneed to WORK not BEG.",{"type":17,"tag":18,"props":102,"children":103},{},[104],{"type":17,"tag":38,"props":105,"children":107},{"alt":7,"src":106},"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/_UYUaEitRq54/SSPfsMnHc-I/AAAAAAAAASM/uqxRJzrQbu0/s400/nobeggingTHU.jpg",[],{"type":17,"tag":18,"props":109,"children":110},{},[111],{"type":46,"value":112},"STOP spreading you hands for money. WORK, if you can.",{"title":7,"searchDepth":114,"depth":114,"links":115},2,[],"markdown","content:blog:please-please-please-stop-begging.md","content","blog/please-please-please-stop-begging.md","blog/please-please-please-stop-begging","md",1719977716454]